OL,3,CThe village whose television
OL,4,Cexperiment pioneered multi-channel TV
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent
OL,7,FVictoria Grimes has been speaking to
OL,8,FJonathan Brown and Michelle Hornby,
OL,9,Ftwo former presenters on the
OL,10,FWaddington Village TV station.
OL,12,FA small town of just over 1,000 people
OL,13,Fbecame one of the pioneers of modern-
OL,14,Fday satellite TV during an experiment
OL,15,Fin 1990.
