OL,3,CThe village whose television
OL,4,Cexperiment pioneered multi-channel TV
OL,6,FWaddington, in Lancashire, also known
OL,7,Fas 'The Television Village', took part
OL,8,Fin a unique experiment led by Granada
OL,9,FTV where multiple television channels
OL,10,Fwere put inside 32 homes - with
OL,11,Fcameras then put on those watching.
OL,13,FThe experiment wanted to see how
OL,14,Fpeople would react to a sudden
OL,15,Fincrease and variety of programmes on
OL,16,Foffer. The Lancashire locals had five
OL,17,Fweeks with the future of television.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
