OL,3,CThe village whose television
OL,4,Cexperiment pioneered multi-channel TV
OL,6,FThe Ribble Valley villagers'
OL,7,Ftelevisions increased from four
OL,8,Fchannels to 32, making the experiment
OL,9,Fa 'pioneer' of satellite television -
OL,10,Fand creating "the original Gogglebox".
OL,12,FOne of those channels available was
OL,13,FWVTV - the world's smallest TV station
OL,14,F- hitting the headlines instantly
OL,15,Fafter it became the most popular TV
OL,16,Fstation in the world.
OL,18,FTwo of the presenters Jonathan Brown
OL,19,Fand Michelle Hornby said the first
OL,20,Ftime they went live was "terrifying"
OL,21,Fand "nerve-racking".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
