OL,3,CThe village whose television
OL,4,Cexperiment pioneered multi-channel TV
OL,6,F"We had a studio which was in the old
OL,7,FSunday school, so we had an audience
OL,8,Fevery night when we did the show,"
OL,9,FMichelle said.
OL,11,F"We had an old settee and two chairs
OL,12,Fand a little table in the middle. And
OL,13,Fthen the students from Preston college
OL,14,Fand Salford college were doing all the
OL,15,Ffilming for us."
