OL,3,CThe village whose television
OL,4,Cexperiment pioneered multi-channel TV
OL,6,FJonathan reflected on the opening
OL,7,Fnight: "It was terrifying. We felt
OL,8,Flike the eyes of the world were upon
OL,9,Fus. They actually turned out to be
OL,10,Fbecause the first night we filmed, it
OL,11,Fended up on ITN News.
OL,13,F"I was there on the screen and the
OL,14,Fwhole thing went blank - the fuse
OL,15,Fblew. We were famous for the wrong
OL,16,Freasons."
OL,18,F"We had no makeup ladies, no scripts,
OL,19,Fno autocues... nothing.
OL,26,@oD@HOUzD@AOU
