OL,3,CThe village whose television
OL,4,Cexperiment pioneered multi-channel TV
OL,6,F"Just think if it had existed now,
OL,7,Fwe'd have been famous."
OL,9,FThe station's success grew, and the
OL,10,Fvillage even managed to knock
OL,11,FCoronation Street off the top of the
OL,12,Flocal ratings charts.
OL,14,F"There were sports channels, there
OL,15,Fwere porn channels, there were various
OL,16,Fthings, and all the locals were like
OL,17,F'this is like something special'
OL,18,Fbecause at the time there were only
OL,19,Ffour TV channels available," Jonathan
OL,20,Fsaid.
