OL,3,CThe village whose television
OL,4,Cexperiment pioneered multi-channel TV
OL,6,F"We'd gone from four to 32."
OL,8,FThe scheme proved so popular everyone
OL,9,Fwanted to get involved - Richard, who
OL,10,Fwas 10 at the time, was one of the
OL,11,Flocal children involved in the
OL,12,Ftelevision series, creating their own
OL,13,Fmini-soap, devised, written and
OL,14,Fstarring in by the village's children.
OL,16,FHe said: "They asked who wanted to do
OL,17,Fa bit of acting on the TV. I'd never
OL,18,Fdone it before."
